'''雷擊性頭痛'''（thunderclap headache，TCH）又稱 '''霹雳性头痛'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.uptodate.com/contents/zh-Hans/overview-of-thunderclap-headache|website=UpToDate|title=霹雳性头痛概述|author=Todd J Schwedt, MD, MSCI|access-date=2021-04-14|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414012718/https://www.uptodate.com/contents/zh-Hans/overview-of-thunderclap-headache|dead-url=no}}</ref>，按定義須滿足兩個條件：<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://doi.org/10.1007/s11910-014-0437-9|title=Thunderclap Headache|first=Esma|last=Dilli|date=2014-03-20|publisher=|journal=Current Neurology and Neuroscience Reports|volume=14|issue=4|pages=437|via=Springer Link|doi=10.1007/s11910-014-0437-9}}</ref>
* 瞬間發作且如爆炸性的嚴重頭痛
* 在60秒內達疼痛頂點，此時痛覺評分為7分以上

==病因==
病因多樣化，且分為原發性與次發性。原發性約占75%，而不致命；次發性的有些會危及性命，如[[蛛網膜下腔出血|蛛網膜下腔出血]]。<ref>{{cite journal|url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16781992/|title=Thunderclap headache|first1=Todd J.|last1=Schwedt|first2=Manjit S.|last2=Matharu|first3=David W.|last3=Dodick|date=2006-07-01|publisher=|journal=The Lancet. Neurology|volume=5|issue=7|pages=621–631|via=PubMed|doi=10.1016/S1474-4422(06)70497-5|pmid=16781992|access-date=2021-04-14|archive-date=2021-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520182213/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16781992/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 原發性：緊縮型頭痛、偏頭痛、三叉自律神經頭痛
* 次發性：蜘蛛膜下腔出血、腦靜脈竇血栓、頸部動脈剝離、高血壓急症、自發性顱內低壓、中風、腦膜炎、可逆性腦血管收縮症候群

